== Welcome

#slide[
  = Welcome, contributors.
  We are a group of systems programmers, compiler enthusiasts, graphics programmers (and just curious people in general) who want to learn by building something real.

  \

  *Our Goals:*
  - Rediscover the *joy of programming* for its own sake.
  - Do deep *systems programming* together in a collaborative environment.
  - Learn how to effectively *build in open source*.
  - Create *resume-worthy projects* (though that's just a happy side-product).
]
